page.html:
[16/3/2017] Luminal V2 - Only 2 hours later from my previous PB, I ONLY GONE DONE DID IT! I am super
happy atm, and thanks to everyone who motivated me in achieving this awesome personal feat. love ya lads <3.

I also would like to thank SleepyDarkrai for the indirect motivation he gave and someone who was a personal osu!mania target of mine, as sad as it is to see him go, through bad times and good, it's for the best. Today of all days, the day he quits is the day I achieved Luminal. I wish all the luck in the near future with a long healthy life, hope everything turns out alright, I'm sure it will. x



Recordings of achievements

Barely scraped Luminal, woo! road to Tachyon begins



Got this second try! Tachyon V2 1/4 files done.
2 Indians as "BANG RIOT"

These 2 damn legends
Origin of BAHLEGDA

Please never do this if you try a Jamaican accent, you clearly get possessed by Satin for a few seconds.


Hey! I am an active 4Ko!m player ONLY. I aim to eventually reach the highest rank 4K!

I come from FFR, that is my first ever VSRG (not inc. Guitar Hero) which I played for about 4 months prior to O!M, so I haven't really been playing the VSRG genre for very long really. I also used to play Guitar Hero drums for a fair few years - stopped around 2010-11, so that explains why I use the Guitar Hero skin. Guitar Hero was my first ever rhythm game, so I simply have to use a skin that is similar, one to which I was born into the rhythm game genre with! I hope to eventually become a top player, I don't mean a known popular player, something more of a personal feat, something that I can truly be proud of as I have never put as much effort into anything else other than this game, so it would be a waste to stop now haha - not only that, I just also find this game incredibly addictive and fun!

I stream rarely, whether it's Facebook or Twitch, you'll always see me around shamelessly advertising if I do
[https://www.twitch.tv/wyvern_ziltoid]

- Current Dan achievements 96% -
[COMPLETE] 8th Dan -
[COMPLETE] 9th Dan -
[COMPLETE] 10th Dan - score / menu
[COMPLETE] Luminal V2 - score / menu
[INCOMPLETE] Tachyon V3/V2

Feel free if you want to PM me your custom maps so that I can give you feedback, I would be more than willing to help out take care!
